---
description: "Quality gates: C type-safety, D security baseline, F performance budget"
alwaysApply: true
---

Non-negotiable gates:

Gate C (Type-safety)
- Web: typecheck must be clean
- API: PHPStan must be clean

Gate D (Security baseline)
- Secrets scan must be clean (gitleaks)
- SAST light must be clean (semgrep auto) OR documented+approved
- Dependency audits: pnpm audit --prod, composer audit

Gate F (Performance budget)
- v1: bundle-size budget must PASS against baseline
- Build must succeed

If a gate cannot run because scripts/config are missing, create the missing scripts/config as the FIRST task (bootstrap tooling).
